和东南亚&lt;/a&gt;派遣员工或专业设备的难度。为什么？这可能是为了阻止他们因预期美国关税更高&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5b45b38c3f124f3c8a9abb9db7542492&amp;amp;_e=6PpeAQ4JXCf2kdBycWtWxM-Nk9xFANzQnNeRCz8uDxfWXLjSYOmCJsAJbkDJCq1iFUBWOGxwVs6JQFyilTlG9pcQdtL9Bc0LMgDYNNEElUovDYC7FeUHOFnVZa8kbIGjGw2ggriylHJvftzFE6u_Ig8RFKUStMT7RbSgY7VKJZ9bFd608gkljeSC2-4A6p5zUpU26PBs1sLYR2D_CBKE89UdlCVfgVmMm461AAxwAmj55S-xgeZogPhP_31egNOj_6oEvFU7BTx2Y04cKw21yTDGj4FTfSL1sIzuMeEUk8_cBjlaLv6AYvdQpmFfi_ZxfYiidQfyhQ8UfjK-2V88T_5YUB0U1BKoKW-OZzejXIXo5iVwPNHM5QX9hxMFqVxZugicGqshD8acSYK1Fjq92a6UB9nCYZhMPU53Nyq-cZhQCPgHR3OIxxmzdc0m-xBIicRS5naUePa6pUsO-I-C38gs6SvTJgoLCjjZ7o0cIvsSBcQ3Ti0lgW_D2BSu8a7IkkVvfEkHpIxIcoiuLG7wSsyzpiz3zBorPLIyQudAVRhVmcVeF9-Mtivkdc_gr1QOw_yDMzi-jNTekWIjT6s9xIsKUlEpCF5hX38C0Jk8ItSjcGTBBYgAluH9bt95i2k_vpfbT5_NY1IQaAoV3EgorT4kAz_Rowezs05CiSSs7hfWCQ-3Kp6owWJi3oJj4LzWWoVpwUKWfjprtS7TD3qYGySb45KsijJzy4YXlpAPsr8vC-oUy4O41aepXNkTzzXCA23vifcSnRIjniIeG2xLCn9xnfnHBUSyF46oDG1TZJQ%3D" target="_blank"&gt;而转移生产&lt;/a&gt;。据称，北京官员鼓励监管机构和地方政府限制向这些地区的技术转让和设备出口。其目的是支撑中国自己的生产，减少可能的裁员，并防止外国投资者逃离中国。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding-bottom: 18px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5b45b38c3f124f3c8a9abb9db7542492&amp;amp;_e=6PpeAQ4JXCf2kdBycWtWxM-Nk9xFANzQnNeRCz8uDxe3TwqNmRwlCd-Hm6Zl759URIPipDfEFRtr8T